Package: moostr
Title: Moodle Syntax String for Multichoice and Numerical Question Types
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Iris",
           family = "Jiang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "iris.jiang@mq.edu.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3708-9574")),
           person("Thomas", "Fung", role = "aut",
           email = "thomas.fung.dr@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8235-1845"))
           )
Description: This package generates a Moodle syntax string for a given list of
    possible answers and their corresponding rewards. It allows the user to conveniently
    allocate rewards for multiple correct and partially correct answers.The package
    also randomly shuffles the answer list for multichoice questions.
